# User Personas

This directory contains user persona definitions for spec review.

Personas are created by running `/init-project` which will ask about your users.

## Persona Format

Each persona file should define:
- Name and role
- Goals and motivations
- Pain points
- Workflows and use cases
- Technical proficiency
- Accessibility needs

## Example

See `.claude/personas/example-persona.md` for format reference.
